<p>Efficiency for a receiver isn’t just about the total yardage that they get. Jaxon Smith-Njigba has developed into a very reliable target for Seahawks quarterback Sam Darnold, thanks to his elite separation and ability to make difficult catches look easy. One of the key statistics that highlights this is his catch rate percentage amongst other top receivers in the NFL. Smith-Njigba, who is top 3 in the NFL in catch rate behind two all-wideouts, makes him a key part in keeping drives and plays alive.</p>
