<p>As you can see in the chart, Jamar Chase, Amon Ra St.&nbsp;Brown, and Puka Nacua led the league in volume, but Jaxon Smith-Njigba maximized every opportunity that came his way. He, in turn, added more production this year on less receptions than any other top receiver in the league at the position, this year showing again how efficient he is. That is what efficiency is all about doing more with less.</p>
